DIGEST
SB 95 Original 2026 Regular Session Edmonds
Present law provides for different types of charter schools according to their authorizer
(either a local school board or BESE) and the proposal and authorization process for each,
which varies depending on the type of school.
Present law also provides that a Type 2 charter school is a BESE-authorized charter school
that operates pursuant to a contract between a nonprofit corporation and BESE. Present law
also provides the conditions under which a charter school can be proposed to BESE as a
